long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
SEO Optimax AI Pro is a cutting-edge Chrome extension designed to enhance your website's search engine optimization (SEO) with powerful AI-driven tools. This all-in-one SEO solution helps you:

Highlight H Tags (H1, H2, H3, etc.): Easily identify and analyze your webpage's header tags for better structure and ranking.
Image and URL Checker: Ensure that all images and URLs on your site are functioning correctly and properly optimized for search engines.
Meta Tag Analyzer: Quickly check meta titles, descriptions, and keywords to improve your site's SEO performance.
AI-Powered Insights: Leverage AI technology for smart suggestions and real-time SEO feedback to boost visibility. Comming soon 
Perfect for web developers, digital marketers, and SEO professionals, SEO Optimax AI Pro is your go-to tool for optimizing web content and improving rankings effortlessly.
